    - target: {fileID: 987798316143663276, guid: afa74880e4f2d0742b9824e803b4536c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Catch as many fish as possible before the timer runs out so you can
        brag to your friends. Press spacebar at the time indicated on the bar to
        catch a fish. Gain 10 Sisu for every fish caught, lose 5 Sisu every time
        you miss.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 987798316143663276, guid: afa74880e4f2d0742b9824e803b4536c, type: 3}
